[SPEAKER_01] ne treba biti, to će mu samo biti teret u životu.

267
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] Treba biti zadovoljan iznutra.

268
00:30:42,519 --> 00:30:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad to imaš u planu, ono, daj, šta si ti, Đu,

