[SPEAKER_01] Jer jako rijetko to vidiš da obstane na taj način,

1158
01:16:18,800 --> 01:16:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] ali mislim da je Ivica pridoneo tome jako puno.

1159
01:16:23,880 --> 01:16:25,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam laka osoba,

1160
01:16:25,640 --> 01:16:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] bez obzira, mislim, ne bi napisala knjigu,

1161
01:16:27,920 --> 01:16:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] napravila 14 ajromena i sve to skupa da sam jednostavna.

1162
01:16:32,939 --> 01:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, evo, on me voli tako kako jesam

1163
01:16:36,000 --> 01:16:37,380
[SPEAKER_01] i strašno me razumije.

1164
01:16:37,380 --> 01:16:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] I velika mi je, velika mi je podrška.

1165
01:16:40,800 --> 01:16:44,560
[SPEAKER_01] I kad čuti, ja kužim šta on misli

1166
01:16:44,560 --> 01:16:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] i on zna šta ja mislim,

1167
01:16:46,159 --> 01:16:49,399
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako je nepotrebno, nećemo to izgovoriti.

1168
01:16:49,399 --> 01:16:55,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je on također vrlo bitan i važan i uspišan muškarac.

1169
01:16:55,479 --> 01:16:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, mislim, nećemo biti, nećemo si lagati,

1170
01:16:59,000 --> 01:17:00,979
[SPEAKER_01] ali ženski libido ide na to.

1171
01:17:01,600 --> 01:17:04,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ženski libido ne ide na napuhanog dečka

1172
01:17:04,560 --> 01:17:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji ima mišiće i ne znam šta,

1173
01:17:07,239 --> 01:17:08,600
[SPEAKER_01] ima ziro u glavi.

1174
01:17:08,600 --> 01:17:11,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, to ne postoji.

1175
01:17:11,020 --> 01:17:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ženski libido ide,

1176
01:17:12,579 --> 01:17:14,020
[SPEAKER_01] ona je iz pećine,

1177
01:17:14,020 --> 01:17:15,520
[SPEAKER_01] ko donese veći plijen,

1178
01:17:15,520 --> 01:17:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno sad govorim o mentalnoj strani.

1179
01:17:18,079 --> 01:17:20,140
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je strašno mentalna strana,

1180
01:17:20,140 --> 01:17:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači može uzbuditi.

1181
01:17:22,079 --> 01:17:23,319
[SPEAKER_01] kad je neko pametan.

1182
01:17:23,319 --> 01:17:26,359
[SPEAKER_01] E, onda kad je neko još pametniji od mene,

1183
01:17:26,359 --> 01:17:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] onda je to, ono,

1184
01:17:27,699 --> 01:17:28,779
[SPEAKER_01] orgazam.

1185
01:17:28,779 --> 01:17:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, ovaj,

1186
01:17:31,119 --> 01:17:36,779
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da smo mi žene tu daleko više evoluirale

1187
01:17:36,779 --> 01:17:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] po tom pitanju.

1188
01:17:40,460 --> 01:17:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] meni nikad nikog,

1189
01:17:43,420 --> 01:17:46,859
[SPEAKER_01] za koga smatram da baš nije previše pametan,

1190
01:17:46,859 --> 01:17:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ne znam koliko je bogat ili šta vozi ili nešto.

1191
01:17:50,619 --> 01:17:52,060
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, mogu se sam smijati,

1192
01:17:52,060 --> 01:17:55,239
[SPEAKER_01] ne otići spavat s takvim čovjekom

1193
01:17:55,239 --> 01:17:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] ili biti uzbuđena s takvim čovjekom.

1194
01:17:57,380 --> 01:17:58,460
[SPEAKER_01] To, to, to,

1195
01:17:58,460 --> 01:17:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] to, to,

1196
01:17:59,380 --> 01:18:01,439
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam bila najmlađa mi nije bilo.

1197
01:18:01,439 --> 01:18:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ženski libido u većini

1198
01:18:04,079 --> 01:18:05,760
[SPEAKER_01] ide na uspješne muškarce.

1199
01:18:05,760 --> 01:18:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je to sad pamet ili je to materialno,

1200
01:18:08,220 --> 01:18:09,899
[SPEAKER_01] to je sad druga stvar,

1201
01:18:09,899 --> 01:18:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] ovisno ženi šta želi

1202
01:18:11,500 --> 01:18:12,939
[SPEAKER_01] i na kojem je nivou,

1203
01:18:12,939 --> 01:18:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali mislim da kod

1204
01:18:15,460 --> 01:18:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] pametnih žena,

1205
01:18:17,319 --> 01:18:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] pametni muškarci prolaze.

1206
01:18:19,000 --> 01:18:20,520
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1207
01:18:20,520 --> 01:18:23,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ivica je najpoznatiji hrvatski vinar,

1208
01:18:23,300 --> 01:18:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

1209
01:18:23,739 --> 01:18:24,439
[SPEAKER_00] Među najpoznatiji.

1210
01:18:24,439 --> 01:18:25,439
[SPEAKER_00] Među najpoznatiji.

1211
01:18:25,439 --> 01:18:30,680
[SPEAKER_01] On ne voli su velike hvaljenja i tako.

1212
01:18:30,680 --> 01:18:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je,

1213
01:18:32,880 --> 01:18:36,100
[SPEAKER_01] on je, on je jak i jak elanac

1214
01:18:36,100 --> 01:18:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] u Istri karika

1215
01:18:39,300 --> 01:18:41,100
[SPEAKER_01] tog postizanja

1216
01:18:41,100 --> 01:18:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] toliko velike vrijednosti Malvazije

1217
01:18:44,380 --> 01:18:48,939
[SPEAKER_01] i samog tog organizirane,

1218
01:18:48,939 --> 01:18:51,060
[SPEAKER_01] organizirane, znači,

1219
01:18:51,060 --> 01:18:53,640
[SPEAKER_01] vinarske regije

1220
01:18:53,640 --> 01:18:56,199
[SPEAKER_01] koja je izuzetno uspješna

1221
01:18:56,199 --> 01:18:57,880
[SPEAKER_01] i najuspješnija u Hrvatskoj.

1222
01:18:57,880 --> 01:19:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da njegova ta obsesija

1223
01:19:02,619 --> 01:19:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] svojim vinogradima

1224
01:19:04,720 --> 01:19:06,319
[SPEAKER_01] i svojim vinom

1225
01:19:06,319 --> 01:19:08,739
[SPEAKER_01] je meni strašno uzbudljiva.

1226
01:19:09,319 --> 01:19:11,840
[SPEAKER_01] ja ponekad znam vi kad tebi je vinograd

1227
01:19:11,840 --> 01:19:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] najbitnije cvjeti, ti ne bi primijetio da ja nestanem,

1228
01:19:15,840 --> 01:19:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] ja u biti obožavam to.

1229
01:19:17,760 --> 01:19:19,100
[SPEAKER_01] zato što nije na meni.

1230
01:19:19,100 --> 01:19:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ne sisava iz mene nekakvu, nego ima svoju obsesiju, ima svoju strast i znam da stvarno to živi i to mi je nešto što mi jako puno znači.

1231
01:19:34,319 --> 01:19:38,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Djurjice, ovi Iron Mani su zapravo vaši Iron Mani.

1232
01:19:38,640 --> 01:19:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da, on je u svakom,

1233
01:19:39,920 --> 01:19:44,060
[SPEAKER_00] bili mogla bez njega, bez njegove organizacije, logistike.

1234
01:19:44,060 --> 01:19:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] Bi.

1235
01:19:44,739 --> 01:19:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bi.

1236
01:19:46,539 --> 01:19:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] Sjajno.

1237
01:19:47,739 --> 01:19:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim,

1238
01:19:49,960 --> 01:19:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] on je zaista

1239
01:19:52,500 --> 01:19:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] jedna podrška

1240
01:19:54,840 --> 01:19:56,560
[SPEAKER_01] koja je, vjerovatno

1241
01:19:56,560 --> 01:19:58,479
[SPEAKER_01] zavijedila sam ju da ju imam.

1242
01:19:58,479 --> 01:20:00,399
[SPEAKER_01] Kad neko kažu tako,

1243
01:20:00,399 --> 01:20:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] dosta ti, recimo,

1244
01:20:01,760 --> 01:20:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] zavidni ljudi, žene, muškarci,

1245
01:20:04,500 --> 01:20:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] pa lako njoj kad ima njega.

1246
01:20:06,079 --> 01:20:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ko? Zašto ti nemaš?

1247
01:20:08,279 --> 01:20:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što nisi zavrijedila

1248
01:20:09,579 --> 01:20:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] ili zavrijedio da imaš nekog takvog.

1249
01:20:11,739 --> 01:20:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] Hajde, zavrijedi.

1250
01:20:13,800 --> 01:20:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] Budi iskren.

1251
01:20:14,699 --> 01:20:20,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ljudi uvijek traže nekakve razloge zašto je neko.

1252
01:20:20,699 --> 01:20:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] To što se ja dižem,

1253
01:20:22,420 --> 01:20:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] u četiri ujutro idem na trening,

1254
01:20:24,500 --> 01:20:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam već u osam doma,

1255
01:20:26,800 --> 01:20:27,779
[SPEAKER_01] kad se svi bude,

1256
01:20:27,779 --> 01:20:29,359
[SPEAKER_01] napravim smuti,

1257
01:20:29,359 --> 01:20:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] popijemo kavu, obožavam to i odem u optiku.

1258
01:20:32,279 --> 01:20:34,399
[SPEAKER_01] To nikom nije bitno.

1259
01:20:34,399 --> 01:20:36,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači što svaki dan treniram,

1260
01:20:37,920 --> 01:20:41,140
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan jebeno plivam u tom bazenu,

1261
01:20:41,140 --> 01:20:42,840
[SPEAKER_01] pre slanom, pre toplom,

1262
01:20:42,840 --> 01:20:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] da radim tehniku od koje nema pomoći,

1263
01:20:45,699 --> 01:20:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] jer sam naučila u 49. godini

1264
01:20:47,380 --> 01:20:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] plivat kraul, pa uvijek

1265
01:20:49,159 --> 01:20:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] napravim u trci onako kakav mi je dan,

1266
01:20:51,380 --> 01:20:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] a ne koliko sam vježbala,

1267
01:20:53,220 --> 01:20:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] napravim po 7 kilometara tjedno.

1268
01:20:56,260 --> 01:20:59,039
[SPEAKER_01] i uporna sam u tome i neću odustati.

1269
01:20:59,319 --> 01:21:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači nije važan talent,

1270
01:21:00,699 --> 01:21:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] nego disciplina i upornosti.

1271
01:21:02,380 --> 01:21:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jako, jako.

1272
01:21:03,539 --> 01:21:04,420
[SPEAKER_01] Najviše.

1273
01:21:04,420 --> 01:21:07,979
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ništa nije važnije

1274
01:21:07,979 --> 01:21:10,659
[SPEAKER_01] u triatlonu od upornosti.

1275
01:21:10,659 --> 01:21:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] I ono između ostalog,

1276
01:21:13,380 --> 01:21:16,479
[SPEAKER_01] što sam najviše ponosna na sebe

1277
01:21:16,479 --> 01:21:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] u mom sportskom životu,

1278
01:21:18,739 --> 01:21:20,760
[SPEAKER_01] su moji treninzi.

1279
01:21:21,699 --> 01:21:23,439
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, u ovih 11 godina

1280
01:21:23,439 --> 01:21:25,359
[SPEAKER_01] ja svaki dan treniram.

1281
01:21:25,359 --> 01:21:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je strašno.

1282
01:21:28,000 --> 01:21:30,020
[SPEAKER_01] To su strašni kilometri.

1283
01:21:30,020 --> 01:21:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja 11 godina se trudim

1284
01:21:32,800 --> 01:21:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] da budim tu gdje jesam.

1285
01:21:34,159 --> 01:21:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ni samo zbog rezultata,

1286
01:21:36,699 --> 01:21:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego da sebi dokažem

1287
01:21:38,500 --> 01:21:39,479
[SPEAKER_01] da ja to mogu.

1288
01:21:39,479 --> 01:21:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] A obužavam to.

1289
01:21:41,539 --> 01:21:44,399
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ja ne mogu zamisliti.

1290
01:21:44,399 --> 01:21:45,920
[SPEAKER_01] To je čista ovisnost.

1291
01:21:45,920 --> 01:21:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja kažem trčanje je laka droga,

1292
01:21:48,300 --> 01:21:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] a triatlon je teška droga.

1293
01:21:50,420 --> 01:21:51,520
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je to,

1294
01:21:51,520 --> 01:21:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] to je razlika.

1295
01:21:53,039 --> 01:21:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ovisna o tome.

1296
01:21:55,579 --> 01:21:56,899
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi kad god putujemo,

1297
01:21:56,899 --> 01:21:58,640
[SPEAKER_01] vozimo biciklu sa mnom,

1298
01:21:58,640 --> 01:22:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] ja moram napraviti.

1299
01:22:00,680 --> 01:22:02,760
[SPEAKER_01] Onda on kad rezervira smješta

1300
01:22:02,760 --> 01:22:04,760
[SPEAKER_01] i gleda da ima bazen za plivanje.

1301
01:22:04,760 --> 01:22:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ovo, ono je znači.

1302
01:22:06,500 --> 01:22:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] I on me uvijek podržava.

1303
01:22:08,159 --> 01:22:09,220
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nije rekao,

1304
01:22:09,220 --> 01:22:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] joj, ili ako imamo nešto dogovoreno,

1305
01:22:11,579 --> 01:22:12,520
[SPEAKER_01] ja kažem, ne mogu sutra,

1306
01:22:12,520 --> 01:22:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] imam duga čak trening,

1307
01:22:13,619 --> 01:22:14,520
[SPEAKER_01] goditi sam,

1308
01:22:14,520 --> 01:22:16,119
[SPEAKER_01] a daj obeća sa načem,

1309
01:22:16,119 --> 01:22:16,939
[SPEAKER_01] onda od skupa,

1310
01:22:16,939 --> 01:22:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] masu puta kažem,

1311
01:22:18,619 --> 01:22:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] žao mi je.

1312
01:22:19,340 --> 01:22:20,779
[SPEAKER_01] i on ode sam

1313
01:22:20,779 --> 01:22:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] i znam da mu je neugodno,

1314
01:22:22,960 --> 01:22:25,020
[SPEAKER_01] da su svi došli u parovima,

1315
01:22:25,020 --> 01:22:26,760
[SPEAKER_01] da je on sad sam tamo.

1316
01:22:26,760 --> 01:22:28,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ali on me razumije,

1317
01:22:28,100 --> 01:22:29,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali on me iskreno razumije.

1318
01:22:29,739 --> 01:22:31,640
[SPEAKER_01] Iskreno me razumije,

1319
01:22:31,640 --> 01:22:32,939
[SPEAKER_01] koliko god je muškarac,

1320
01:22:32,939 --> 01:22:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali je različit muškarac.

1321
01:22:35,800 --> 01:22:37,720
[SPEAKER_01] muškarac koji čini razliku.

1322
01:22:37,720 --> 01:22:42,619
[SPEAKER_01] I jako sam sretna što smo se tako slučajno,

1323
01:22:42,619 --> 01:22:44,479
[SPEAKER_01] na Vinistri smo se upoznali

1324
01:22:44,479 --> 01:22:46,439
[SPEAKER_01] i kako smo se upoznali,

1325
01:22:46,439 --> 01:22:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] nismo se razvojili,

1326
01:22:47,539 --> 01:22:48,260
[SPEAKER_01] da slavu se.

1327
01:22:48,260 --> 01:22:51,279
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ti znači njegova podrška?

1328
01:22:51,399 --> 01:22:51,859
[SPEAKER_00] sjećam se,

1329
01:22:51,859 --> 01:22:53,340
[SPEAKER_00] u knjizi si opisala trenutak,

1330
01:22:53,340 --> 01:22:55,180
[SPEAKER_00] prvi kad neće kaš se da,

1331
01:22:55,180 --> 01:22:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad misleš da li možeš ti triatlon,

1332
01:22:57,279 --> 01:22:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] ma ne,

1333
01:22:57,579 --> 01:22:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš ti triatlon.

1334
01:22:58,659 --> 01:23:00,520
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi put kad si...

1335
01:23:00,520 --> 01:23:02,060
[SPEAKER_01] Da, u poreču kad je bilo,

1336
01:23:02,060 --> 01:23:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam htjela duatlon odraditi,

1337
01:23:03,659 --> 01:23:04,659
[SPEAKER_01] privanje i trčanje.

1338
01:23:04,659 --> 01:23:06,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si htjela duatlon i on je rekao...

1339
01:23:06,439 --> 01:23:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne znam od me,

1340
01:23:07,300 --> 01:23:09,699
[SPEAKER_01] on me je nagovorio doslovce na triatlon.

1341
01:23:09,699 --> 01:23:11,779
[SPEAKER_01] Da, on je rekao,

1342
01:23:11,779 --> 01:23:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] kupit ćemo svu oprenu,

1343
01:23:13,159 --> 01:23:14,319
[SPEAKER_01] nećeš raditi duatlon,

1344
01:23:14,319 --> 01:23:15,359
[SPEAKER_01] radit ćeš triatlon.

1345
01:23:15,359 --> 01:23:16,060
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš ti to?

1346
01:23:16,060 --> 01:23:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš ti to.

1347
01:23:16,859 --> 01:23:20,100
[SPEAKER_01] U 15 dana se spremi za dugi triatlon.

1348
01:23:20,100 --> 01:23:22,979
[SPEAKER_01] 110 kilometara je bilo.

1349
01:23:22,979 --> 01:23:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] To nijedan luđaka.

1350
01:23:24,699 --> 01:23:25,140
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1351
01:23:25,140 --> 01:23:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što ja imam poremeća jedan,

1352
01:23:27,239 --> 01:23:28,479
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne znam lijevo desno

1353
01:23:28,479 --> 01:23:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ne mogu vizualizirati kvadrate,

1354
01:23:31,420 --> 01:23:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] ni kilometre.

1355
01:23:32,300 --> 01:23:33,859
